{
  "info": {
    "name": "Integration Modul Aparat API",
    "_postman_id": "integration-aparat-v2",
    "description": "# üöÄ Integration Modul Aparat API Collection\n\n## üìù Cara Penggunaan:\n\n### 1Ô∏è‚É£ Setup Environment\n- Collection ini menggunakan **Collection Variables**\n- `baseUrl` default: `http://localhost:3000`\n- Tokens akan auto-save setelah Login/Register\n\n### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Authentication Flow\n1. **Register** atau **Login** ‚Üí Tokens auto-saved\n2. Semua endpoint (kecuali Auth) otomatis pakai `accessToken`\n3. Jika token expired, gunakan **Refresh Token**\n\n### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Testing Flow\n```\nRegister/Login ‚Üí Get Profile ‚Üí CRUD Operations ‚Üí Logout\n```\n\n## üîë Variables:\n- `baseUrl`: Base URL API (default: http://localhost:3000)\n- `accessToken`: JWT Access Token (auto-saved, expires 30m)\n- `refreshToken`: JWT Refresh Token (auto-saved, expires 7d)\n\n## üìö Modules:\n- ‚úÖ Authentication (Public)\n- üîí Aparat (Protected)\n- üîí Ekspedisi (Protected)\n- üîí Surat (Protected)\n- üîí Events (Protected)\n- üîí Users (Protected)\n- ‚úÖ Health Check (Public)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{accessToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
